1. *Moraće*š da se trudiš ako želiš da položiš ispit. (You will have to try hard if you want to pass the exam.)
2. Ne znam kada će *moraće*da počnem sa pripremama za put. (I don't know when I will have to start preparing for the trip.)
3. *Moraće*da idemo ranije ako želimo stići na vreme. (We will have to leave earlier if we want to arrive on time.)
4. *Moraće*da ga nazovete da biste dobili više informacija. (You will have to call him to get more information.)
5. Ako *moraće*da ostanemo kod kuće zbog lošeg vremena, možemo igrati društvene igre. (If we have to stay home because of bad weather, we can play board games.)
6. *Moraće*da se suočiš sa posledicama svojih postupaka. (You will have to face the consequences of your actions.)
7. Nadam se da *moraće*da ne čekamo predugo na red. (I hope we don't have to wait too long in line.)
8. *Moraće*da ponesemo kišobrane ako najavljuju padavine. (We will have to bring umbrellas if they are forecasting rain.)
9. Za uspešan završetak projekta, *moraće*da se svi uključe u rad. (For a successful project completion, everyone will have to get involved in the work.)
10. *Moraće*da pronađemo alternativni put ako je glavna ulica blokirana. (We will have to find an alternate route if the main street is blocked.)